{"BEQUEATH":[{"def":"To give or leave by will; to give by testament; -- said especially of personal property.","pos":""},{"def":"To hand down; to transmit.","pos":""}],"BEQUEATHABLE":[{"def":"Capable of being bequeathed.","pos":""}],"BEQUEATHAL":[{"def":"The act of bequeathing; bequeathment; bequest.","pos":""}],"BEQUEATHMENT":[{"def":"The act of bequeathing, or the state of being bequeathed; a bequest.","pos":""}],"BEQUEST":[{"def":"The act of bequeathing or leaving by will; as, a bequest of property by A.","pos":""},{"def":"That which is left by will, esp.","pos":""}],"BEQUETHEN":[{"def":"Be*queth\"en, Defn: old p.","pos":""}],"BEQUOTE":[{"def":"To quote constantly or with great frequency.","pos":""}]}